the family to make the declaration.</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">To pass on the change of address, you need a valid identity document with your national registration number.</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">If an unattended minor leaves his parents' residence for the first time to establish his main residence elsewhere, he must be accompanied by someone exercising parental authority.</p><h3 data-indentation-level=\"0\" __rdfaid=\"9343e89d-d54c-41ad-8698-415ed9aad428\">Checking domicile and updating identity documents</h3><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">After the declaration, a neighbourhood police officer or an authorised official checks whether you actually have your main residence at the declared address. After this check, you will be registered at your new address and invited to the town hall to have your identity card adapted. For this, you will need your electronic identity card with pin code.</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">From the moment your identity card is adapted, you can inform all other authorities of your change of address.</p><h3 data-indentation-level=\"0\" __rdfaid=\"116d85db-daf2-481b-92ff-e0542b9da937\">Vehicle registration certificate</h3><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">The change of address no longer needs to be applied to the vehicle registration certificate of your vehicle(s). The registration certificate will only state the address that was valid at the time of issue.</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\"></p>","en":"<p data-indentation-level=\"0\">a</p>","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"<p data-indentation-level=\"0\"></p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">U moet de adreswijziging melden aan de gemeente waar het nieuwe adres gelegen is:</p><ul __rdfaid=\"26cdb90f-62e3-40bb-b641-01fdc679cb6f\"><li __rdfaid=\"6303dd02-e3b0-4544-849e-85dca9cf8de9\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">U kunt de adreswijziging online melden via het digitaal loket van uw (nieuwe) gemeente.</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"fa1beccb-04c5-450a-aa6f-64b8ec6e4cda\"><p data-indentat